	<topic>Using Embedded Owner-Draw Specifications in Controls</topic>
<description>There are techniques for including bitmaps and font information in the data displayed by various Xdialog controls. This lesson will show you how you can embed an owner draw directive directly in the data that you are displaying. In many cases this will greatly simplify using fonts and images in your controls.</description>	
